headline: S&P Dow Jones Indices to Acquire ARC Research, Expanding Wealth Data and Benchmarking Capabilities
summary: S&P Dow Jones Indices ("S&P DJI"), a division of S&P Global (NYSE: SPGI) and the world's leading index provider, today announced that it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire ARC Research, a subsidiary of ARC Group, and the leading independent provider of investment performance data, benchmarking capabilities and insights in the private wealth market.
